content: yungalgo: Focused on core project infrastructure and packaging, merging a significant fix in `elizaos/eliza#5882` to scope npm package fields for registry entries (+8532/-499 lines). They also improved the developer experience by adding Docker files to the project starter in `elizaos/eliza#5858` and submitted 11 new plugins to the `elizaos-plugins/registry`. This work shows a primary focus on configuration files and core project code, complemented by providing feedback on 6 pull requests.
